Author: poppybasket
Text: !!! it really be this way. would be a hilarious irony if it didn’t literally ruin our every day lives

Author: BladderPatrol
Text: I overate cabbage I had made for dinner and then took a bunch of bites of my boyfriend’s curry takeout dinner. I felt so gross and guilty so I purged and while I had my head buried in the toilet I thought ‘if I had a real problem I wouldn’t have eaten the food in the first place’
